{"text_id":215695,"tokens":["The"," Fermi"," Paradox"," and"," Great"," Filter"," hypothesis"," are"," two"," related"," concepts"," that"," attempt"," to"," explain"," the"," apparent"," absence"," of"," intelligent"," life"," in"," the"," universe","."," The"," Fermi"," Paradox"," refers"," to"," the"," contradiction"," between"," the"," high"," probability"," of"," the"," existence"," of"," extrater","restrial"," civilizations"," and"," the"," lack"," of"," evidence"," for"," their"," presence","."," The"," Great"," Filter"," hypothesis"," pos","its"," that"," there"," are"," one"," or"," more"," obstacles"," that"," prevent"," civilizations"," from"," becoming"," interstellar"," and"," thus"," explaining"," the"," Fermi"," Paradox",".","\n\n","The"," Fermi"," Paradox"," and"," Great"," Filter"," hypothesis"," have"," been"," widely"," discussed"," in"," scientific"," communities"," since"," their"," conception","."," Many"," scientists"," have"," taken"," these"," hypotheses"," seriously"," and"," have"," used"," scientific"," methods"," to"," attempt"," to"," explain"," them","."," The"," study"," of"," astro","biology",","," which"," focuses"," on"," the"," search"," for"," extrater","restrial"," life"," and"," the"," conditions"," necessary"," for"," life"," to"," exist",","," is"," an"," increasingly"," prominent"," field"," that"," has"," contributed"," to"," the"," discussion"," of"," these"," hypotheses","."," ","\n\n","Some"," scientists"," argue"," that"," the"," Fermi"," Paradox"," and"," Great"," Filter"," hypothesis"," provide"," a"," framework"," for"," understanding"," the"," difficulties"," of"," interstellar"," travel"," and"," communication","."," They"," argue"," that"," these"," obstacles"," might"," be"," physical",","," such"," as"," the"," difficulty"," of"," traversing"," the"," vast"," distances"," between"," stars",","," or"," societal",","," such"," as"," the"," potential"," for"," civilizations"," to"," destroy"," themselves"," before"," reaching"," the"," level"," of"," technological"," sophistication"," required"," for"," interstellar"," travel",".","\n\n","However",","," others"," are"," more"," skeptical"," of"," these"," hypotheses","."," They"," argue"," that"," the"," Fermi"," Paradox"," may"," be"," the"," result"," of"," our"," limited"," technology"," and"," perspective","."," They"," suggest"," that"," perhaps"," we"," have"," not"," yet"," discovered"," evidence"," of"," extrater","restrial"," life"," because"," we"," are"," simply"," not"," advanced"," enough"," to"," detect"," it",".","\n\n","Despite"," these"," differing"," opinions",","," the"," Fermi"," Paradox"," and"," Great"," Filter"," hypothesis"," continue"," to"," be"," important"," topics"," of"," discussion"," in"," scientific"," communities","."," As"," the"," search"," for"," extrater","restrial"," life"," and"," the"," study"," of"," astro","biology"," continue"," to"," advance",","," it"," is"," likely"," that"," these"," hypotheses"," will"," continue"," to"," be"," examined"," and"," refined","."],"sub_source":"reddit","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}